  · exact LinearSieveRoughDyadicMultiplesSignedErrorAbsQuarterBound_of_signed
  · exact LinearSieveRoughDyadicMultiplesSignedErrorQuarterBound_of_abs

/-- The rough-count Euler-product discrepancy package implies the symmetric
