    a₀ b₀ C₀).mpr
    ⟨linear_sieve_rough_dyadic_count_lower_bound a₀ b₀ C₀ ha₀ hab,
      linear_sieve_rough_dyadic_count_upper_bound a₀ b₀ C₀ ha₀ hab⟩

/-- Manuscript-shaped name for the dyadic rough squarefree count input.

All reciprocal estimates below are derived from this count-level statement by
checked dyadic partial summation. -/
